			Opticians, and also offers leasing opportunities to Licensed
			Optometrists. Our optical departments consistently deliver an
			industry-leading level of service and value, and are staffed by
			trained professionals. If a career opportunity with Pawsco Optical
			interests you, please apply online for optician positions. For
			leasing opportunities, email Denise Mogil <a href="#">dmogil@Pawsco.com</a>.<br>
			<br> Pawsco is looking for Licensed Hearing Aid Dispensers and
			Dispensing Audiologists who want to build their careers with one of
			the largest independent hearing aid retailers in the United States.
			We have a need for full-time (40 hours per week) as well as part-time
			(24 hours per week) licensed professionals. For employment
			opportunities in our hearing aid centers, please send your resume to
			Tammy Miller <a href="#">tammymiller@Pawsco.com</a>.<br> <br>
			Pawsco is currently seeking Licensed Pharmacists to fill positions
			for pharmacy managers and full time, part time and relief/floating
			pharmacist positions. Pawsco ranks as one of the top 10 drug chains
			nationally and we currently operate more than 480 pharmacies,
			employing 1,800 pharmacists. For career opportunities, please <a
